ance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Link_link__0e2efd CDS_Link_noUnderline__0e2efd" href="/reviews/696dda065fd8b422f79ff350" rel="nofollow" data-review-title-typography="true"><h2 class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681" data-service-review-title-typography="true">Spliff ist genial</h2></a><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-l__68c681" data-service-review-text-typography="true">Spliff ist genial. Ich bin sehr glücklich, dieses aus Zufall im Internet gefunden zu haben. Extrem zuverlässig :-) Clara kommuniziert immer sehr freundlich, kompetent und zeitnah. Gute Qualität, super Verpackung. Diskret. Gesund. Hilft bei körperlichen Schmerzen .Ein tolles Team - Danke :-)</p><div class="styles_reviewBadges__Rmr_i"><div class="styles_badgesContainer__4pZPJ"><div class="CDS_Badge_badge__083901 CDS_Badge_s__083901 CDS_Badge_variant-subtle__083901 CDS_Badge_type-default__083901" data-testid="review-badge-date"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">14. Jänner 2026</span></div><div class="CDS_Badge_badge__083901 CDS_Badge_s__083901 CDS_Badge_variant-subtle__083901 CDS_Badge_type-default__083901" data-testid="review-badge-unprompted"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">Bewertung ohne vorherige Einladung</span></div></div></div></div></section><div class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a CDS_Card_borderRadius-m__146e7a styles_wrapper__WD_1K"><div><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="38" viewBox="0 0 14 38" fill="none"><path d="M1 1V25C1 31.6274 6.37258 37 13 37V37" stroke="#E5E5DD" stroke-