 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">Bewertung ohne vorherige Einladung</span></div></div></div></div></section><div class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a CDS_Card_borderRadius-m__146e7a styles_wrapper__WD_1K"><div><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="38" viewBox="0 0 14 38" fill="none"><path d="M1 1V25C1 31.6274 6.37258 37 13 37V37" stroke="#E5E5DD" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"></path></svg></div><div class="styles_content__eJmhl"><div class="styles_replyHeader__zKV_w"><picture class="business-profile-image_containmentWrapper__xJZjr styles_businessLogo__x6IFu" data-cpl="true"><source srcSet="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.avif, https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-2x.avif 2x" type="image/avif"/><source srcSet="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.jpg, https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-2x.jpg 2x" type="image/jpeg"/><img class="business-profile-image_image__V14jr" src="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.jpg" alt="Spliff-Logo" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></picture><div class="styles_replyInfo__41_in"><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 CDS_Typography_weight-heavy__68c681 styles_replyCompany__DgFhD" weight="heavy" data-service-review-business-reply-title-typography="true">Antwort von Spliff</p><time data-cpl="true" dateTime="2026-01-22T15:53:55.000Z" class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681" data-service-review-business-reply-date-time-ago="true">22. Jan. 2026</time></div></div><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 styles_message__jAzYB" data-service-review-business-reply-text-typography="true">Hallo Jürgen,<br/>vielen Dank für Ihr Vertrauen und Ihre Nachricht!<br/>Wir freuen uns, dass wir Ihnen helfen konnten und Sie zufrieden sind. Wir legen großen Wert darauf, die Qualität unserer Produkte und unseren Service zu verbessern. 😊<br/>Wir freuen uns darauf, Sie wieder zu begleiten.<br/><br/>Das Spliff-Team</p></div></div></div></article></div><div class="styles_cardWrapper__g8amG styles_show__Z8n7u"><article class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a styles_reviewCard__Qwhpy" data-service-review-card-paper="true"><div data-testid="service-review-card-v2"><div class="styles_reviewCardInnerHeader__8Xqy8"><aside class="styles_consumerInfoWrapper__6HN5O" aria-label="Infos zu C.Husemann"><div class="styles_consumerDetailsWrapper__4eZod"><div class="CDS_Avatar_avatar__dd7fc3 CDS_Avatar_pink__dd7fc3" style="width:44px;min-width:44px;height:44px;min-height:44px" data-testid="consumer-avatar"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Avatar_avatarName__dd7fc3">C.</span></div><a data-cpl="true" href="/users/6608108717cfe20012d1b2b3" rel="nofollow" name="consumer-profile" target="_self" class="link_internal__Eam_b link_wrapper__ahpyq styles_consumerDetails__POC79" data-consumer-profile-link="true"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681 styles_consumerName__xKr9c" data-consumer-name-typography="true">C.Husemann</span><div class="styles_consumerExtraDetails__NY6RP" data-consumer-reviews-count="6"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681" data-consumer-country-typography="true">DE</span><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-xs__68c681" data-lil-dot-typography="true">•</span><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681" data-consumer-reviews-count-typography="true">6<!-- --> Bewertungen</span></div></a></div></aside><div class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 styles_datesWrapper__jszhG"><time data-cpl="true" dateTime="2026-01-08T16:57:16.000Z" class="" data-service-review-date-time-ago="true">8. Jan. 2026</time></div></div><section class="styles_reviewContentwrapper__K2aRu" aria-disabled="false"><div class="styles_reviewHeader__DzoAZ" data-service-review-rating="5"><img class="CDS_StarRating_starRating__614d2e" alt="Bewertet mit 5 von 5 Sternen" width="108px" src="https://cdn.trustpilot.net/brand-assets/4.1.0/stars/stars-5.svg"/></div><div class="styles_reviewContent__tuXiN" aria-hidden="false" data-review-content="true"><a class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Link_link__0e2efd CDS_Link_noUnderline__0e2efd" href="/reviews/695fc5cc1f25bd7787e15f5a" rel="nofollow" data-review-title-typography="true"><h2 class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681" data-service-review-title-typography="true">Habe schon öfter dort den Sirup…</h2></a><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-l__68c681" data-service-review-text-typography="true">Habe schon öfter dort den Sirup bestellt, der mir bei meinen Depressionen abends zum Abspannen hilft. Da ich kein Weed mehr rauche bzw. generell nicht mehr rauche, kommt der Sirup als Alternative gut daher. Bei meiner letzten Bestellung kam es dank DHL zu Lieferproblemen, der Support von Spliff war in dem Fall sehr schnell und Kundenorientiert und hilfsbereit.Gibt eigentlich nichts zu bemängeln, Ware sowie Service Top ;-)</p><div class="styles_reviewBadges__Rmr_i"><div class="styles_badgesContainer__4pZPJ"><div class="CDS_Badge_badge__083901 CDS_Badge_s__083901 CDS_Badge_variant-subtle__083901 CDS_Badge_type-default__083901" data-testid="review-badge-date"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">8. Jänner 2026</span></div><div class="CDS_Badge_badge__083901 CDS_Badge_s__083901 CDS_Badge_variant-subtle__083901 CDS_Badge_type-default__083901" data-testid="review-badge-unprompted"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">Bewertung ohne vorherige Einladung</span></div></div></div></div></section><div class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a CDS_Card_borderRadius-m__146e7a styles_wrapper__WD_1K"><div><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="38" viewBox="0 0 14 38" fill="none"><path d="M1 1V25C1 31.6274 6.37258 37 13 37V37" stroke="#E5E5DD" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"></path></svg></div><div class="styles_content__eJmhl"><div class="styles_replyHeader__zKV_w"><picture class="business-profile-image_containmentWrapper__xJZjr styles_businessLogo__x6IFu" data-cpl="true"><source srcSet="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.avif, https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-2x.avif 2x" type="image/avif"/><source srcSet="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.jpg, https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-2x.jpg 2x" type="image/jpeg"/><img class="business-profile-image_image__V14jr" src="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.jpg" alt="Spliff-Logo" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></picture><div class="styles_replyInfo__41_in"><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 CDS_Typography_weight-heavy__68c681 styles_replyCompany__DgFhD" weight="heavy" data-service-review-business-reply-title-typography="true">Antwort von Spliff</p><time data-cpl="true" dateTime="2026-01-22T15:41:12.000Z" class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681" data-service-review-business-reply-date-time-ago="true">22. Jan. 2026</time></div></div><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 styles_message__jAzYB" data-service-review-business-reply-text-typography="true">Vielen Dank für Ihr positives Feedback und Ihre Treue 😊<br/>Wir freuen uns, dass Sie mit dem Magic Potion zufrieden sind und dass er für Sie eine gute Alternative darstellt.<br/>Trotz der Lieferprobleme, die außerhalb unserer Kontrolle lagen, sind wir froh, Ihnen schnell helfen zu können.<br/>Bis bald und vielen Dank für Ihr Vertrauen!<br/><br/>Das Spliff-Team</p></div></div></div></article></div><div class="styles_cardWrapper__g8amG styles_show__Z8n7u"><article class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a styles_reviewCard__Qwhpy" data-service-review-card-paper="true"><div data-testid="service-review-card-v2"><div class="styles_reviewCardInnerHeader__8Xqy8"><aside class="styles_consumerInfoWrapper__6HN5O" aria-label="Infos zu Itz_akari-Chan UWU"><div class="styles_consumerDetailsWrapper__4eZod"><div class="CDS_Avatar_avatar__dd7fc3 CDS_Avatar_green__dd7fc3" style="width:44px;min-width:44px;height:44px;min-height:44px" data-testid="consumer-avatar"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Avatar_avatarName__dd7fc3">IU</span></div><a data-cpl="true" href="/users/61e82b58317986001258fdec" rel="nofollow" name="consumer-profile" target="_self" class="link_internal__Eam_b link_wrapper__ahpyq styles_consumerDetails__POC79" data-consumer-profile-link="true"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681 styles_consumerName__xKr9c" data-consumer-name-typography="true">Itz_akari-Chan UWU</span><div class="styles_consumerExtraDetails__NY6RP" data-consumer-reviews-count="5"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681" data-consumer-country-typography="true">DE</span><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-xs__68c681" data-lil-dot-typography="true">•</span><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681" data-consumer-reviews-count-typography="true">5<!-- --> Bewertungen</span></div></a></div></aside><div class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 styles_datesWrapper__jszhG"><time data-cpl="true" dateTime="2025-12-28T20:56:23.000Z" class="" data-service-review-date-time-ago="true">28. Dez. 2025</time></div></div><section class="styles_reviewContentwrapper__K2aRu" aria-disabled="false"><div class="styles_reviewHeader__DzoAZ" data-service-review-rating="5"><img class="CDS_StarRating_starRating__614d2e" alt="Bewertet mit 5 von 5 Sternen" width="108px" src="https://cdn.trustpilot.net/brand-assets/4.1.0/stars/stars-5.svg"/></div><div class="styles_reviewContent__tuXiN" aria-hidden="false" data-review-content="true"><a class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Link_link__0e2efd CDS_Link_noUnderline__0e2efd" href="/reviews/69517d572b742c1f50b84dfc" rel="nofollow" data-review-title-typography="true"><h2 class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681" data-service-review-title-typography="true">Ich habe viel erlebt mit „Clara“</h2></a><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-l__68c681" data-service-review-text-typography="true">Ich habe viel erlebt mit „Clara“.  Ich habe immer Antwort bekommen, meistens nach einem Tag aber auch zwei und auch schon längere Zeit aber es hat sich immer jemand gemeldet, um mir und meiner Bestellung zu helfen. Manche schreiben hier, die Gummibärchen würden nicht knallen, finde ich auch leider, bei jeder meiner Bestellungen ist immer son Gummibärchen dabei, würde ich niemals bestellen, haben null Effekt.. Was ich immer bestelle ist dieser Sirum 300 in verschiedenen Geschmacksrichtungen, wobei der bittere Nachgang bei jedem Schluck schon echt bitter ist. Der Situp knallt gut, bin eigentlich leidenschaftliche kifferin, habe aber mit rauchen aufgehört. Ich bin im Training.wie man so schön sagt.. trotzdem knallt der Sirup sehr gut, ich finde nur irgendwie leider nicht so lange so 3 Stunden aber das mag an der EU und deren Bevormundung und der runter Regulierung liegen.</p><div class="styles_reviewBadges__Rmr_i"><div class="styles_badgesContainer__4pZPJ"><div class="CDS_Badge_badge__083901 CDS_Badge_s__083901 CDS_Badge_variant-subtle__083901 CDS_Badge_type-default__083901" data-testid="review-badge-date"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">28. Dezember 2025</span></div><div class="CDS_Badge_badge__083901 CDS_Badge_s__083901 CDS_Badge_variant-subtle__083901 CDS_Badge_type-default__083901" data-testid="review-badge-unprompted"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">Bewertung ohne vorherige Einladung</span></div></div></div></div></section><div class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a CDS_Card_borderRadius-m__146e7a styles_wrapper__WD_1K"><div><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="38" viewBox="0 0 14 38" fill="none"><path d="M1 1V25C1 31.6274 6.37258 37 13 37V37" stroke="#E5E5DD" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"></path></svg></div><div class="styles_content__eJmhl"><div class="styles_replyHeader__zKV_w"><picture class="business-profile-image_containmentWrapper__xJZjr styles_businessLogo__x6IFu" data-cpl="true"><source srcSet="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.avif, https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-2x.avif 2x" type="image/avif"/><source srcSet="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.jpg, https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-2x.jpg 2x" type="image/jpeg"/><img class="business-profile-image_image__V14jr" src="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.jpg" alt="Spliff-Logo" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></picture><div class="styles_replyInfo__41_in"><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 CDS_Typography_weight-heavy__68c681 styles_replyCompany__DgFhD" weight="heavy" data-service-review-business-reply-title-typography="true">Antwort von Spliff</p><time data-cpl="true" dateTime="2026-01-15T14:50:54.000Z" class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681" data-service-review-business-reply-date-time-ago="true">15. Jan. 2026</time></div></div><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 styles_message__jAzYB" data-service-review-business-reply-text-typography="true">Guten Tag,<br/>vielen Dank für Ihr ausführliches Feedback und Ihre positiven Worte zu Ihrem Austausch mit unserem Service – die Qualität unseres Kundenservices ist für uns von zentraler Bedeutung.<br/>Bezüglich der Gummies haben wir eine Charge identifiziert, die in Bezug auf die Wirkung nicht unseren Erwartungen entsprach. Dieses Problem wurde inzwischen behoben, und die aktuellen Chargen entsprechen wieder vollständig unseren Standards.<br/>Es freut uns sehr, dass Ihnen die Sirupe gefallen. Der leicht bittere Geschmack ist auf die hohe THC-Konzentration zurückzuführen. Die kürzere Wirkungsdauer erklärt sich durch die schnelle Aufnahme aufgrund der Verdauung und der flüssigen Produktform.<br/>Wenn Sie eine länger anhaltende Wirkung suchen, empfehlen wir Ihnen, unsere Brownies zu probieren, deren langsamere Aufnahme in der Regel eine Wirkungsdauer von 4 bis 5 Stunden ermöglicht.<br/>Vielen Dank nochmals für Ihr Vertrauen.<br/><br/>Ihr Spliff-Team</p></div></div></div></article></div><div class="styles_cardWrapper__g8amG styles_show__Z8n7u"><article class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a styles_reviewCard__Qwhpy" data-service-review-card-paper="true"><div data-testid="service-review-card-v2"><div class="styles_reviewCardInnerHeader__8Xqy8"><aside class="styles_consumerInfoWrapper__6HN5O" aria-label="Infos zu Kathleen Kaeuffert"><div class="styles_consumerDetailsWrapper__4eZod"><div class="CDS_Avatar_imageWrapper__dd7fc3" style="width:44px;height:44px;min-width:44px;min-height:44px" data-testid="consumer-avatar"><img alt="" data-consumer-avatar-image="true" loading="lazy" width="44" height="44" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" style="color:transparent" src="https://user-images.trustpilot.com/693feb853d98f013f1f98513/73x73.png"/></div><a data-cpl="true" href="/users/693feb853d98f013f1f98513" rel="nofollow" name="consumer-profile" target="_self" class="link_internal__Eam_b link_wrapper__ahpyq styles_consumerDetails__POC79" data-consumer-profile-link="true"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681 styles_consumerName__xKr9c" data-consumer-name-typography="true">Kathleen Kaeuffert</span><div class="styles_consumerExtraDetails__NY6RP" data-consumer-reviews-count="1"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681" data-consumer-country-typography="true">DE</span><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-xs__68c681" data-lil-dot-typography="true">•</span><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681" data-consumer-reviews-count-typography="true">1<!-- --> Bewertung</span></div></a></div></aside><div class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 styles_datesWrapper__jszhG"><time data-cpl="true" dateTime="2025-12-15T13:05:51.000Z" class="" data-service-review-date-time-ago="true">15. Dez. 2025</time></div></div><section class="styles_reviewContentwrapper__K2aRu" aria-disabled="false"><div class="styles_reviewHeader__DzoAZ" data-service-review-rating="1"><img class="CDS_StarRating_starRating__614d2e" alt="Bewertet mit 1 von 5 Sternen" width="108px" src="https://cdn.trustpilot.net/brand-assets/4.1.0/stars/stars-1.svg"/></div><div class="styles_reviewContent__tuXiN" aria-hidden="false" data-review-content="true"><a class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Link_link__0e2efd CDS_Link_noUnderline__0e2efd" href="/reviews/693feb8e25fa62e56647e73e" rel="nofollow" data-review-title-typography="true"><h2 class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681" data-service-review-title-typography="true">Meine lezter Bestellung war nicht gut</h2></a><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-l__68c681" data-service-review-text-typography="true">Meine lezter Bestellung war nicht gut, habe keine Wirkung gemerkt, bin sehr enttäuscht.  Bestellung von 5 Dezember.  Habe aus Versehen noch 2 mal bestellt,  jetzt sitz ich da mit sch das nicht wirken, habe sogar als Tee getrunken,  auch keine Wirkung und schmecked eklig.  LG KATHLEEN </p><div class="styles_reviewBadges__Rmr_i"><div class="styles_badgesContainer__4pZPJ"><div class="CDS_Badge_badge__083901 CDS_Badge_s__083901 CDS_Badge_variant-subtle__083901 CDS_Badge_type-default__083901" data-testid="review-badge-date"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">15. Dezember 2025</span></div><div class="CDS_Badge_badge__083901 CDS_Badge_s__083901 CDS_Badge_variant-subtle__083901 CDS_Badge_type-default__083901" data-testid="review-badge-unprompted"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">Bewertung ohne vorherige Einladung</span></div></div></div></div></section><div class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a CDS_Card_borderRadius-m__146e7a styles_wrapper__WD_1K"><div><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="38" viewBox="0 0 14 38" fill="none"><path d="M1 1V25C1 31.6274 6.37258 37 13 37V37" stroke="#E5E5DD" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"></path></svg></div><div class="styles_content__eJmhl"><div class="styles_replyHeader__zKV_w"><picture class="business-profile-image_containmentWrapper__xJZjr styles_businessLogo__x6IFu" data-cpl="true"><source srcSet="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.avif, https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-2x.avif 2x" type="image/avif"/><source srcSet="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.jpg, https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-2x.jpg 2x" type="image/jpeg"/><img class="business-profile-image_image__V14jr" src="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.jpg" alt="Spliff-Logo" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></picture><div class="styles_replyInfo__41_in"><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 CDS_Typography_weight-heavy__68c681 styles_replyCompany__DgFhD" weight="heavy" data-service-review-business-reply-title-typography="true">Antwort von Spliff</p><time data-cpl="true" dateTime="2026-01-22T16:12:00.000Z" class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681" data-service-review-business-reply-date-time-ago="true">22. Jan. 2026</time></div></div><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 styles_message__jAzYB" data-service-review-business-reply-text-typography="true">Hallo Kathleen,<br/>vielen Dank, dass Sie sich die Zeit genommen haben, Ihre Erfahrungen mit uns zu teilen. Es tut uns aufrichtig leid, dass Ihre Bestellung vom 5. Dezember nicht Ihren Erwartungen entsprochen hat und Sie nicht die gewünschten Ergebnisse erzielt haben.<br/><br/>Jeder Mensch kann unterschiedlich auf unsere Produkte reagieren, da mehrere Faktoren ihre Wirksamkeit beeinflussen können (Anwendungsweise, Dauer, Dosierung usw.). <br/>Ich möchte Sie auch darauf hinweisen, dass es notwendig ist, Ihrer Zubereitung ein Fett (Milch, Öl...) hinzuzufügen, da Cannabinoide sich nicht in Wasser auflösen. Es ist daher normal, dass Sie durch den alleinigen Aufguss der Blüten keine Wirkung spüren.  <br/>Außerdem möchte ich daran erinnern, dass CBD in erster Linie eine entspannende und keine psychoaktive Wirkung hat. Wenn Sie eine stärkere Alternative bevorzugen, empfehlen wir Ihnen unsere THCX-Produktreihe.<br/>Unser Team steht unseren Kunden jederzeit zur Verfügung, um sie zu begleiten und bestmöglich zu beraten.<br/><br/>Wir haben auch festgestellt, dass Sie kürzlich eine weitere Bestellung aufgegeben haben, wofür wir uns herzlich bedanken. Wir hoffen, dass Sie mit dieser neuen Erfahrung voll und ganz zufrieden sein werden.<br/><br/>Zögern Sie nicht, unseren Kundenservice zu kontaktieren, um eine auf Ihr Profil zugeschnittene Beratung zu erhalten.<br/>Wir stehen Ihnen jederzeit zur Verfügung und wünschen Ihnen einen schönen Tag.<br/><br/>Das Spliff-Team</p></div></div></div></article></div><div class="styles_cardWrapper__g8amG styles_show__Z8n7u"><article class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a styles_reviewCard__Qwhpy" data-service-review-card-paper="true"><div data-testid="service-review-card-v2"><div class="styles_reviewCardInnerHeader__8Xqy8"><aside class="styles_consumerInfoWrapper__6HN5O" aria-label="Infos zu Kay Sachse"><div class="styles_consumerDetailsWrapper__4eZod"><div class="CDS_Avatar_imageWrapper__dd7fc3" style="width:44px;height:44px;min-width:44px;min-height:44px" data-testid="consumer-avatar"><img alt="" data-consumer-avatar-image="true" loading="lazy" width="44" height="44" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" style="color:transparent" src="https://user-images.trustpilot.com/64e07a5aad2b1c001324f6b2/73x73.png"/></div><a data-cpl="true" href="/users/64e07a5aad2b1c001324f6b2" rel="nofollow" name="consumer-profile" target="_self" class="link_internal__Eam_b link_wrapper__ahpyq styles_consumerDetails__POC79" data-consumer-profile-link="true"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681 styles_consumerName__xKr9c" data-consumer-name-typography="true">Kay Sachse</span><div class="styles_consumerExtraDetails__NY6RP" data-consumer-reviews-count="4"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681" data-consumer-country-typography="true">DE</span><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-xs__68c681" data-lil-dot-typography="true">•</span><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681" data-consumer-reviews-count-typography="true">4<!-- --> Bewertungen</span></div></a></div></aside><div class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 styles_datesWrapper__jszhG"><time data-cpl="true" dateTime="2025-12-06T23:30:09.000Z" class="" data-service-review-date-time-ago="true">6. Dez. 2025</time></div></div><section class="styles_reviewContentwrapper__K2aRu" aria-disabled="false"><div class="styles_reviewHeader__DzoAZ" data-service-review-rating="4"><img class="CDS_StarRating_starRating__614d2e" alt="Bewertet mit 4 von 5 Sternen" width="108px" src="https://cdn.trustpilot.net/brand-assets/4.1.0/stars/stars-4.svg"/></div><div class="styles_reviewContent__tuXiN" aria-hidden="false" data-review-content="true"><a class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Link_link__0e2efd CDS_Link_noUnderline__0e2efd" href="/reviews/6934a0618572ba3dee85309c" rel="nofollow" data-review-title-typography="true"><h2 class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681" data-service-review-title-typography="true">Bis jetzt kann ich nur bestätigen das…</h2></a><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-l__68c681" data-service-review-text-typography="true">Bis jetzt kann ich nur bestätigen das es gut ist und manchmal auch besser laufen kann wenn man es mit der DHL versenden würde </p><div class="styles_reviewBadges__Rmr_i"><div class="styles_badgesContainer__4pZPJ"><div class="CDS_Badge_badge__083901 CDS_Badge_s__083901 CDS_Badge_variant-subtle__083901 CDS_Badge_type-default__083901" data-testid="review-badge-date"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">6. Dezember 2025</span></div><div class="CDS_Badge_badge__083901 CDS_Badge_s__083901 CDS_Badge_variant-subtle__083901 CDS_Badge_type-default__083901" data-testid="review-badge-unprompted"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">Bewertung ohne vorherige Einladung</span></div></div></div></div></section><div class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a CDS_Card_borderRadius-m__146e7a styles_wrapper__WD_1K"><div><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="38" viewBox="0 0 14 38" fill="none"><path d="M1 1V25C1 31.6274 6.37258 37 13 37V37" stroke="#E5E5DD" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"></path></svg></div><div class="styles_content__eJmhl"><div class="styles_replyHeader__zKV_w"><picture class="business-profile-image_containmentWrapper__xJZjr styles_businessLogo__x6IFu" data-cpl="true"><source srcSet="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.avif, https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-2x.avif 2x" type="image/avif"/><source srcSet="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.jpg, https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-2x.jpg 2x" type="image/jpeg"/><img class="business-profile-image_image__V14jr" src="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.jpg" alt="Spliff-Logo" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></picture><div class="styles_replyInfo__41_in"><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 CDS_Typography_weight-heavy__68c681 styles_replyCompany__DgFhD" weight="heavy" data-service-review-business-reply-title-typography="true">Antwort von Spliff</p><time data-cpl="true" dateTime="2026-01-08T10:03:35.000Z" class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681" data-service-review-business-reply-date-time-ago="true">8. Jan. 2026</time></div></div><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 styles_message__jAzYB" data-service-review-business-reply-text-typography="true">Hallo Kay, <br/><br/>vielen Dank für Ihr Feedback! Wir freuen uns, dass Sie mit unseren Produkten zufrieden sind. Ihre Anmerkung bezüglich des bevorzugten Logistikdienstleisters haben wir zur Kenntnis genommen und werden sie zur weiteren Verbesserung nutzen.<br/>Bei Fragen stehen wir Ihnen gerne zur Verfügung.<br/>Das Spliff-Team</p></div></div></div></article></div><div class="styles_cardWrapper__g8amG styles_show__Z8n7u"><article class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a styles_reviewCard__Qwhpy" data-service-review-card-paper="true"><div data-testid="service-review-card-v2"><div class="styles_reviewCardInnerHeader__8Xqy8"><aside class="styles_consumerInfoWrapper__6HN5O" aria-label="Infos zu Kunde HH Eidelstedt"><div class="styles_consumerDetailsWrapper__4eZod"><div class="CDS_Avatar_avatar__dd7fc3 CDS_Avatar_green__dd7fc3" style="width:44px;min-width:44px;height:44px;min-height:44px" data-testid="consumer-avatar"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Avatar_avatarName__dd7fc3">KH</span></div><a data-cpl="true" href="/users/6345387007d7b20014c284f4" rel="nofollow" name="consumer-profile" target="_self" class="link_internal__Eam_b link_wrapper__ahpyq styles_consumerDetails__POC79" data-consumer-profile-link="true"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681 styles_consumerName__xKr9c" data-consumer-name-typography="true">Kunde HH Eidelstedt</span><div class="styles_consumerExtraDetails__NY6RP" data-consumer-reviews-count="9"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681" data-consumer-country-typography="true">DE</span><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-xs__68c681" data-lil-dot-typography="true">•</span><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681" data-consumer-reviews-count-typography="true">9<!-- --> Bewertungen</span></div></a></div></aside><div class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 styles_datesWrapper__jszhG"><time data-cpl="true" dateTime="2025-11-20T16:46:14.000Z" class="" data-service-review-date-time-ago="true">20. Nov. 2025</time></div></div><section class="styles_reviewContentwrapper__K2aRu" aria-disabled="false"><div class="styles_reviewHeader__DzoAZ" data-service-review-rating="5"><img class="CDS_StarRating_starRating__614d2e" alt="Bewertet mit 5 von 5 Sternen" width="108px" src="https://cdn.trustpilot.net/brand-assets/4.1.0/stars/stars-5.svg"/></div><div class="styles_reviewContent__tuXiN" aria-hidden="false" data-review-content="true"><a class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Link_link__0e2efd CDS_Link_noUnderline__0e2efd" href="/reviews/691f29b6b97d424267af52ad" rel="nofollow" data-review-title-typography="true"><h2 class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681" data-service-review-title-typography="true">Super Vapes, toller Service, gerne wieder!</h2></a><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-l__68c681" data-service-review-text-typography="true">Erstens sind alle Produkte von Spliff wirklich gut. Zweitens hatte ich eine Reklamation zur einem der Vapes und Pods und habe sofort ganz unkompliziert Ersatz zugeschickt bekommen. Das freut mich sehr, weil die Dinger wirklich klasse sind! Aber vorsichtig anfangen, da steckt wirklich power hinter! Danke!</p><div class="styles_reviewBadges__Rmr_i"><div class="styles_badgesContainer__4pZPJ"><div class="CDS_Badge_badge__083901 CDS_Badge_s__083901 CDS_Badge_variant-subtle__083901 CDS_Badge_type-default__083901" data-testid="review-badge-date"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">20. November 2025</span></div><div class="CDS_Badge_badge__083901 CDS_Badge_s__083901 CDS_Badge_variant-subtle__083901 CDS_Badge_type-default__083901" data-testid="review-badge-unprompted"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">Bewertung ohne vorherige Einladung</span></div></div></div></div></section><div class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a CDS_Card_borderRadius-m__146e7a styles_wrapper__WD_1K"><div><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="38" viewBox="0 0 14 38" fill="none"><path d="M1 1V25C1 31.6274 6.37258 37 13 37V37" stroke="#E5E5DD" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"></path></svg></div><div class="styles_content__eJmhl"><div class="styles_replyHeader__zKV_w"><picture class="business-profile-image_containmentWrapper__xJZjr styles_businessLogo__x6IFu" data-cpl="true"><source srcSet="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.avif, https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-2x.avif 2x" type="image/avif"/><source srcSet="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.jpg, https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-2x.jpg 2x" type="image/jpeg"/><img class="business-profile-image_image__V14jr" src="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.jpg" alt="Spliff-Logo" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></picture><div class="styles_replyInfo__41_in"><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 CDS_Typography_weight-heavy__68c681 styles_replyCompany__DgFhD" weight="heavy" data-service-review-business-reply-title-typography="true">Antwort von Spliff</p><time data-cpl="true" dateTime="2026-01-22T15:42:15.000Z" class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681" data-service-review-business-reply-date-time-ago="true">22. Jan. 2026</time></div></div><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 styles_message__jAzYB" data-service-review-business-reply-text-typography="true">Hallo,<br/>vielen Dank für Ihr begeistertes Feedback! Wir freuen uns sehr, dass Ihnen unsere Vapes und unser Service gefallen haben. Sie haben Recht: Der Magic Vape mit der höchsten THCX-Konzentration in unserem Sortiment ist eine ausgezeichnete Wahl für erfahrene Konsumenten.<br/>Gute Nachrichten: In den nächsten Wochen werden neue Geschmacksrichtungen erhältlich sein. Wir hoffen, dass sie Ihnen gefallen werden!<br/><br/>Das Spliff-Team</p></div></div></div></article></div><div class="styles_cardWrapper__g8amG styles_show__Z8n7u"><article class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a styles_reviewCard__Qwhpy" data-service-review-card-paper="true"><div data-testid="service-review-card-v2"><div class="styles_reviewCardInnerHeader__8Xqy8"><aside class="styles_consumerInfoWrapper__6HN5O" aria-label="Infos zu Oliver Rudolf"><div class="styles_consumerDetailsWrapper__4eZod"><div class="CDS_Avatar_imageWrapper__dd7fc3" style="width:44px;height:44px;min-width:44px;min-height:44px" data-testid="consumer-avatar"><img alt="" data-consumer-avatar-image="true" loading="lazy" width="44" height="44" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" style="color:transparent" src="https://user-images.trustpilot.com/6911142451678e8bfa8c03fa/73x73.png"/></div><a data-cpl="true" href="/users/6911142451678e8bfa8c03fa" rel="nofollow" name="consumer-profile" target="_self" class="link_internal__Eam_b link_wrapper__ahpyq styles_consumerDetails__POC79" data-consumer-profile-link="true"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681 styles_consumerName__xKr9c" data-consumer-name-typography="true">Oliver Rudolf</span><div class="styles_consumerExtraDetails__NY6RP" data-consumer-reviews-count="1"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681" data-consumer-country-typography="true">DE</span><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-xs__68c681" data-lil-dot-typography="true">•</span><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681" data-consumer-reviews-count-typography="true">1<!-- --> Bewertung</span></div></a></div></aside><div class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 styles_datesWrapper__jszhG"><time data-cpl="true" dateTime="2025-11-10T00:22:35.000Z" class="" data-service-review-date-time-ago="true">10. Nov. 2025</time></div></div><section class="styles_reviewContentwrapper__K2aRu" aria-disabled="false"><div class="styles_reviewHeader__DzoAZ" data-service-review-rating="1"><img class="CDS_StarRating_starRating__614d2e" alt="Bewertet mit 1 von 5 Sternen" width="108px" src="https://cdn.trustpilot.net/brand-assets/4.1.0/stars/stars-1.svg"/></div><div class="styles_reviewContent__tuXiN" aria-hidden="false" data-review-content="true"><a class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Link_link__0e2efd CDS_Link_noUnderline__0e2efd" href="/reviews/6911142b30a74a92f15cda04" rel="nofollow" data-review-title-typography="true"><h2 class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681" data-service-review-title-typography="true">Die Lieferungen sind fehlerhaft</h2></a><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-l__68c681" data-service-review-text-typography="true">Die Lieferungen sind fehlerhaft, auf Nachfragen wird nicht reagiert,  geld wird einfach einbehalten obwohl die qaren zurück ging laut DHL </p><div class="styles_reviewBadges__Rmr_i"><div class="styles_badgesContainer__4pZPJ"><div class="CDS_Badge_badge__083901 CDS_Badge_s__083901 CDS_Badge_variant-subtle__083901 CDS_Badge_type-default__083901" data-testid="review-badge-date"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">1. November 2025</span></div><div class="CDS_Badge_badge__083901 CDS_Badge_s__083901 CDS_Badge_variant-subtle__083901 CDS_Badge_type-default__083901" data-testid="review-badge-unprompted"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">Bewertung ohne vorherige Einladung</span></div></div></div></div></section><div class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a CDS_Card_borderRadius-m__146e7a styles_wrapper__WD_1K"><div><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="38" viewBox="0 0 14 38" fill="none"><path d="M1 1V25C1 31.6274 6.37258 37 13 37V37" stroke="#E5E5DD" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"></path></svg></div><div class="styles_content__eJmhl"><div class="styles_replyHeader__zKV_w"><picture class="business-profile-image_containmentWrapper__xJZjr styles_businessLogo__x6IFu" data-cpl="true"><source srcSet="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.avif, https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-2x.avif 2x" type="image/avif"/><source srcSet="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.jpg, https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-2x.jpg 2x" type="image/jpeg"/><img class="business-profile-image_image__V14jr" src="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.jpg" alt="Spliff-Logo" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></picture><div class="styles_replyInfo__41_in"><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 CDS_Typography_weight-heavy__68c681 styles_replyCompany__DgFhD" weight="heavy" data-service-review-business-reply-title-typography="true">Antwort von Spliff</p><time data-cpl="true" dateTime="2026-01-22T16:13:44.000Z" class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681" data-service-review-business-reply-date-time-ago="true">22. Jan. 2026</time></div></div><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 styles_message__jAzYB" data-service-review-business-reply-text-typography="true">Hallo Oliver,<br/><br/>vielen Dank für Ihre Nachricht. Nach Ihrem Gespräch mit unserem Kundenservice wurde Ihre Bestellung erneut versandt. Wir entschuldigen uns nochmals für die Unannehmlichkeiten, die Ihnen durch den Spediteur entstanden sind.<br/>Wir haben festgestellt, dass Sie anschließend mehrere Bestellungen aufgegeben haben, die ohne Zwischenfälle geliefert wurden, was uns sehr freut. <br/>Unser gesamtes Team ist täglich bemüht, die Qualität unserer Produkte und Dienstleistungen zu verbessern. Aus diesem Grund haben wir eine Partnerschaft mit einem neuen Transportunternehmen geschlossen, von dem wir hoffen, dass es Sie zufriedenstellen wird.<br/>Selbstverständlich stehen wir Ihnen bei Bedarf jederzeit zur Verfügung.<br/><br/>Das Spliff-Team</p></div></div></div></article></div><div class="styles_cardWrapper__g8amG styles_show__Z8n7u"><article class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a styles_reviewCard__Qwhpy" data-service-review-card-paper="true"><div data-testid="service-review-card-v2"><div class="styles_reviewCardInnerHeader__8Xqy8"><aside class="styles_consumerInfoWrapper__6HN5O" aria-label="Infos zu Rapfanatik Ultra"><div class="styles_consumerDetailsWrapper__4eZod"><div class="CDS_Avatar_avatar__dd7fc3 CDS_Avatar_green__dd7fc3" style="width:44px;min-width:44px;height:44px;min-height:44px" data-testid="consumer-avatar"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Avatar_avatarName__dd7fc3">RU</span></div><a data-cpl="true" href="/users/5fd220f033b62e0019430cae" rel="nofollow" name="consumer-profile" target="_self" class="link_internal__Eam_b link_wrapper__ahpyq styles_consumerDetails__POC79" data-consumer-profile-link="true"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681 styles_consumerName__xKr9c" data-consumer-name-typography="true">Rapfanatik Ultra</span><div class="styles_consumerExtraDetails__NY6RP" data-consumer-reviews-count="6"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681" data-consumer-country-typography="true">DE</span><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-xs__68c681" data-lil-dot-typography="true">•</span><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681" data-consumer-reviews-count-typography="true">6<!-- --> Bewertungen</span></div></a></div></aside><div class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 styles_datesWrapper__jszhG"><time data-cpl="true" dateTime="2025-11-03T12:03:02.000Z" class="" data-service-review-date-time-ago="true">3. Nov. 2025</time></div></div><section class="styles_reviewContentwrapper__K2aRu" aria-disabled="false"><div class="styles_reviewHeader__DzoAZ" data-service-review-rating="1"><img class="CDS_StarRating_starRating__614d2e" alt="Bewertet mit 1 von 5 Sternen" width="108px" src="https://cdn.trustpilot.net/brand-assets/4.1.0/stars/stars-1.svg"/></div><div class="styles_reviewContent__tuXiN" aria-hidden="false" data-review-content="true"><a class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Link_link__0e2efd CDS_Link_noUnderline__0e2efd" href="/reviews/69087dd695eadb340ac3062a" rel="nofollow" data-review-title-typography="true"><h2 class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681" data-service-review-title-typography="true">Lieferung kommt nicht an</h2></a><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-l__68c681" data-service-review-text-typography="true">Hallo. <br/><br/>Ich habe etwas auf der Website bestellt (Sirup) und darauf mehrere Tage gewartet, als es laut DPD endlich abgeholt wurde, stand dort plötzlich, dass das Paket nicht zugestellt werden konnte und dass das Paket zurück an den Absender geschickt wird. <br/>Weder war DPD bei mir, noch krieg man irgendeine Info vom Spliffstore. Ich habe im vorausbezahlt und kriege weder online, noch anderswo Informationen.<br/>Paket kommt nicht und Geld ist weg. <br/>Für mich sind die Bewertung hier alle Fake und der Shop Scam. <br/>Nie wieder werd ich bei den bestellen, da kann ich das Geld auch anzünden. </p><div class="styles_reviewBadges__Rmr_i"><div class="styles_badgesContainer__4pZPJ"><div class="CDS_Badge_badge__083901 CDS_Badge_s__083901 CDS_Badge_variant-subtle__083901 CDS_Badge_type-default__083901" data-testid="review-badge-date"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">1. November 2025</span></div><div class="CDS_Badge_badge__083901 CDS_Badge_s__083901 CDS_Badge_variant-subtle__083901 CDS_Badge_type-default__083901" data-testid="review-badge-unprompted"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-inherit__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Badge_badgeText__083901">Bewertung ohne vorherige Einladung</span></div></div></div></div></section><div class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a CDS_Card_borderRadius-m__146e7a styles_wrapper__WD_1K"><div><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="38" viewBox="0 0 14 38" fill="none"><path d="M1 1V25C1 31.6274 6.37258 37 13 37V37" stroke="#E5E5DD" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"></path></svg></div><div class="styles_content__eJmhl"><div class="styles_replyHeader__zKV_w"><picture class="business-profile-image_containmentWrapper__xJZjr styles_businessLogo__x6IFu" data-cpl="true"><source srcSet="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.avif, https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-2x.avif 2x" type="image/avif"/><source srcSet="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.jpg, https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-2x.jpg 2x" type="image/jpeg"/><img class="business-profile-image_image__V14jr" src="https://consumersiteimages.trustpilot.net/business-units/65a8f486fe59a0421a2a19f2-198x149-1x.jpg" alt="Spliff-Logo" loading="lazy" decoding="async"/></picture><div class="styles_replyInfo__41_in"><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 CDS_Typography_weight-heavy__68c681 styles_replyCompany__DgFhD" weight="heavy" data-service-review-business-reply-title-typography="true">Antwort von Spliff</p><time data-cpl="true" dateTime="2026-01-29T13:02:13.000Z" class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-s__68c681" data-service-review-business-reply-date-time-ago="true">29. Jan. 2026</time></div></div><p class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681 styles_message__jAzYB" data-service-review-business-reply-text-typography="true">Guten Tag,<br/><br/>wir bedauern diese schlechte Erfahrung sehr und verstehen Ihre Unzufriedenheit.<br/><br/>Es kam insbesondere bei unseren Sendungen mit dem Postdienst DPD zu Lieferproblemen. Aus diesem Grund haben wir unseren Logistikpartner gewechselt, um die Zuverlässigkeit und Qualität unseres Services zu verbessern. Unsere ersten Eindrücke von den jüngsten Sendungen sind ausgezeichnet. <br/><br/>Seien Sie versichert, dass unser Kundenservice Ihnen gerne zur Verfügung steht, um die Situation zu klären. Zögern Sie nicht, uns unter Angabe Ihrer Bestellnummer zu kontaktieren.<br/><br/>Das Team von Spliffstore</p></div></div></div></article></div><div class="styles_cardWrapper__g8amG styles_show__Z8n7u"><article class="CDS_Card_card__146e7a styles_reviewCard__Qwhpy" data-service-review-card-paper="true"><div data-testid="service-review-card-v2"><div class="styles_reviewCardInnerHeader__8Xqy8"><aside class="styles_consumerInfoWrapper__6HN5O" aria-label="Infos zu Daniel Schöpe"><div class="styles_consumerDetailsWrapper__4eZod"><div class="CDS_Avatar_avatar__dd7fc3 CDS_Avatar_pink__dd7fc3" style="width:44px;min-width:44px;height:44px;min-height:44px" data-testid="consumer-avatar"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681 CDS_Typography_disableResponsiveSizing__68c681 CDS_Avatar_avatarName__dd7fc3">DS</span></div><a data-cpl="true" href="/users/6640bc7b6da07cfaaf1bcf43" rel="nofollow" name="consumer-profile" target="_self" class="link_internal__Eam_b link_wrapper__ahpyq styles_consumerDetails__POC79" data-consumer-profile-link="true"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-default__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_heading-xs__68c681 styles_consumerName__xKr9c" data-consumer-name-typography="true">Daniel Schöpe</span><div class="styles_consumerExtraDetails__NY6RP" data-consumer-reviews-count="1"><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681" data-consumer-country-typography="true">DE</span><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-xs__68c681" data-lil-dot-typography="true">•</span><span class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c681 CDS_Typography_body-m__68c681" data-consumer-reviews-count-typography="true">1<!-- --> Bewertung</span></div></a></div></aside><div class="CDS_Typography_appearance-subtle__68c681 CDS_Typography_prettyStyle__68c68